# Jupyter Notebook outputs (keep notebooks, ignore execution artifacts)
# Prevent large binary files from executed notebooks
**/notebooks/**/*.png
**/notebooks/**/*.jpg
**/notebooks/**/*.jpeg
**/notebooks/**/*.gif
**/notebooks/**/*.pdf
**/notebooks/**/*.h5
**/notebooks/**/*.hdf5
**/notebooks/**/*.tif
**/notebooks/**/*.tiff
**/notebooks/**/*.nitf
**/notebooks/**/*.cphd
**/notebooks/**/*.npz
**/notebooks/**/*.npy
# But allow small documentation images
!docs/images/*.png
!docs/images/*.jpg
!example_images/*.png
!example_images/*.jpg

